= FactHarbor =

{{box title="TL;DR: What is FactHarbor?"}}
🎯 **Mission**: Bring clarity to contested information through transparent, AI-powered reasoning.
💡 **Innovation**: We don't just give a "True/False" label; we map the entire **Evidence Landscape** with explicit assumptions and confidence scores.
⚖️ **Values**: Non-profit, open-source, and strictly evidence-based.
{{/box}}

